-- Cabral dos Santos May Join Portugal Telecom Board, Jornal Says
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-03-26T07:58:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/cabral-dos-santos-may-join-portugal-telecom-board-jornal-says.html
Caixa Geral de Depositos SA ,
 Portugal ’s state-owned bank, may appoint Jose Pedro Cabral dos
Santos to the board of  Portugal Telecom SGPS SA (PTC) ,  Jornal de
Negocios  reported, without saying how it obtained the
information.  Cabral dos Santos would be one of Caixa Geral’s
representatives on the board of Portugal Telecom after the
nomination of former Finance Minister Fernando Teixeira dos Santos was rejected by the government, according to the
Portuguese newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
 halmeida5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
